name: Franklin Elementary School VRV IVS
scope_statement:
F&I two (2) Four (4) ton split systems for the four classrooms at Franklin ES. 
DBSG will rig units to the roof and install wall brackets per walk-thru.
DBSG will hang and mount four (4) 24,000 BTU indoor ceiling round flow units per submittal, one (10  in each classroom.
DBSG will install interconnecting refrigeration piping as required to connect indoor units to outdoor condensers. (Two indoor units per condenser)
DBSG will provide micropump condensate pumps for each indoor unit and discharge condensate to the rooftop.
SPS to provide electrical power and control wiring as required.
SPS to provide pitch pockets for piping penetrations through the roof area.
SPS to re-configure drop ceiling and tiles as required after installation.
DBSG to evacuate and charge units for proper operation after installation.
DBSC to start-up systems and provide one (1) year installation warranty on installation.
Daikin Applied to provide the manufacturer's warranty on the equipment.
